-- Volcano on Argentina-Chile Border Spits Ash, La Tercera Says
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r i s t o w
-- 2012-12-22T16:48:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-22/volcano-on-argentina-chile-border-spits-ash-la-tercera-says.html
Copahue volcano on the border of
Argentina and  Chile  is emitting clouds of ash, La Tercera
 reported , citing Mines Minister Hernan de Solminihac.  The activity was on the Argentine side of the border, the
Santiago-based newspaper reported on its website. Chilean
authorities declared an orange alert, which restricts flights in
the area, La Tercera reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Bristow in Bogota at 
 mbristow5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Philip Sanders at 
 psanders@bloomberg.net . 